'''Â-pí''' (亞庇, [[Mâ-lòi-ngî]]: Kota Kinabalu) he [[Mâ-lòi-sî-â]] [[Sâ-pâ-chû]] ke sú-fú. Mâ-lòi-sî-â thu̍k-li̍p chṳ̂-chhièn pûn-ngìn chhṳ̂n-cho ''Jesselton''. Kîn-kí chhòn-sot Â-pí he [[Mâ-lòi-ngî]] chûng "[[fó]]" ke yi-sṳ. Pâu-hàm chû-vì ke sàng-chṳ́n khiung-yû chhit-sṳ̍p-van ngìn. Liá-piên ke Mâ-lòi-sî-â fà-ngìn sṳ́-yung [[Hak-kâ-ngî]]. 

